com.blockwithme.util.shared.converters

Class ConverterRegistry

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.blockwithme.util.shared.converters.ConverterRegistry

  • public class ConverterRegistry
extends Object
    ConverterRegistry is a registry for primitive converters. Converters must match the type exactly, because otherwise the "toObject()" conversion would not usually return the correct type. It is thread-safe, and can delegate/fallback to another registry.
